            "title": "修改服務條款惹亦！沃爾瑪、Target等零售巨頭擁抱AI 購物助理出錯卻甩鍋給顧客",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/uKbqUEDTSRtb1VKuoUmLMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/0de7ade9e311a1ddf740b1a3c774f145\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%E6%83%B9%E4%BA%A6-%E6%B2%83%E7%88%BE%E7%91%AA-target%E7%AD%89%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%B7%A8%E9%A0%AD%E6%93%81%E6%8A%B1ai-%E8%B3%BC%E7%89%A9%E5%8A%A9%E7%90%86%E5%87%BA%E9%8C%AF%E5%8D%BB%E7%94%A9%E9%8D%8B%E7%B5%A6%E9%A1%A7%E5%AE%A2-125002493.html",
